"DISTRIBUTOR SCREEN"  HOTKEY = right Amiga + T

In this Screen you put in Information about yourself, like your Name, your
personal Number, your Sponsors name etc.

                              @{" Buttons " LINK DistBut}
                              @{" Fields  " LINK DistFields}
                              @{" Menues  " LINK DistMenus}

@ENDNODE
